    "They are introduced to the vision on how to lighten their workload using assistive tools powered by AI.",
    "ChatGPT is the text generation model that is currently being used, but as new AI chat bots emerge, university staff is testing them and showing students the differences between them.In the subject ASRS, the students are required to submit a projecta software system that they must create and fully document using an iterative process.",
    "Our first use of ChatGPT is when we demonstrate its capabilities for idea generation.As seen on Fig. 1, a description of the problem help is needed with is given on the left, and although it lacks detail, it is a true and valid statement, so the model gives a useful, albeit generic answer.",
